t14.com.GameRentals

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • t14.com.GameRentals.Game
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class contains information for Game objects. Each game has a game name, game ID, descirption, status, list of bids, owner, and borrower. Game status can be either available, bidded, or borrowed. Borrower will be initialized to null and only set if game status is borrowed. Created by cjresler on 2016-02-28.
